[SN]TITLE[SN]
Aaron Tshibola: Nottingham Forest sign Aston Villa midfielder on loan

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Nottingham Forest have signed Aston Villa midfielder Aaron Tshibola on loan for the remainder of the season.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
The 22-year-old joined Villa from Reading in July and has made 10 appearances for the Championship club.
The ex-Hartlepool loanee scored his first senior goal in a 1-1 draw against Newcastle at Villa Park in September.
Villa have signed midfielders Henri Lansbury, Conor Hourihane and Birkir Bjarnason during the January transfer window.
